* {{ill|Meiji (era)|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1872|ja|1872nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shō Tai|ja|尚泰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , King of {{ill|Ryukyu Kingdom|ja|琉球王国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , is officially designated as the "Ryukyu Domain King" and Ranked among the {{ill|Kazoku|ja|華族|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Japanese nobility).
