* {{ill|Manju (era)|ja|万寿|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1027|ja|1027th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 16|ja|10月16日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Genshi|ja|藤原妍子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Empress Chūgū|ja|中宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of {{ill|Emperor Sanjō|ja|三条天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and daughter of {{ill|Fujiwara no Michinaga|ja|Fujiwara no Michinaga|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|994|ja|994th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
