* {{ill|Kan'ei (era)|ja|寛永|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 20 (Gregorian {{ill|1643|ja|1643rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kasuga no Tsubone|ja|春日局|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the wet nurse of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1579|ja|1579th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
